Running Instructions:

    1. Configure your image in the configuration. The program takes the first argument (argv[1]).
    2. Run the program.
    3. First and second LEFT click draw a rectangle.
    4. If you want to redraw the rectangle then RIGHT click one time and go back to (3).
    5. To draw the elliptic curved line LEFT click inside the rectangle.
    6. If want to redraw, RIGHT click one time and go back to (3).
    7. LEFT click one time will execute the transformation.
    8. RIGHT click on the original image closes all windows.
